Babau (buh-BAY-yoo) are greater Tanar'ri who look like horned skeletons with leathery black hides, dripping with blood-red slime. Their role is to herd Petitioners and minor Tanar'ri to feed the armies of the Blood War. 

      Sources:&nbsp;
    
            
                    Planescape Monstrous Compendium, Volume 1        
              
                    Faces of Evil: The Fiends        
              
                    Book of Vile Darkness